{"tid":1833319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"任正非表示美國的打擊未起很大作用　稱華為是親美公司","createTime":"2020-01-21T22:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T01:31:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3fa117a091163f5fb45f6ac5972b7e26fe20a17","tid":1833319,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:36:35.000Z","msg":"任正非表示美國的打擊未起很大作用　稱華為是親美公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504093-20200122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504093-20200122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmK0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=e8fa4192\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504093-20200122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c53b24ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504093-20200122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備商華為創辦人任正非，出席瑞士達沃斯世界經濟論壇，表示美國的打擊並未起到很大作用，華為亦做了大量準備。<br />\n<br />\n被問到美國對中國技術的發展表示擔憂，任正非認為美國是過度憂慮，美國亦因為長期習慣自己是世界老大，而對其他人的發展感到不舒服。<br />\n<br />\n任正非強調，華為能夠成功，都是向美國學習，華為本來就是一間親美的公司，美國應該感到驕傲，又認為全人類都要合作研究科技如何造福人類。"},{"pid":"e3398898ccd3077c83c8d9f62bb00715f658b92f","tid":1833319,"uid":280329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:46:25.000Z","msg":"未起很大作用<br />\n但成功令佢傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1139b8f73e3874ec2a03f899f0fd9cfdb9664c88","tid":1833319,"uid":159047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:48:44.000Z","msg":"Cisco 就真係慘咯"},{"pid":"f88cd9686f41c62c4e2c806c057fbe17a5cc3a43","tid":1833319,"uid":131188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:52:34.000Z","msg":"華為親美，支那民眾係咪要罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d79cb0572f51c43d44ce4c4cf64c94ec8104bf4","tid":1833319,"uid":55854,"like":1,"dislike":0,